### Zero Trust - API Key to JWT Flow

### 1. Obter JWT usando API Key do time IA
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
X-API-KEY: chave-ia

### 2. Obter JWT usando API Key do time IOT
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
X-API-KEY: chave-iot

### 3. Obter JWT usando API Key do time JAVA
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
X-API-KEY: chave-java

### 4. Obter JWT usando API Key do time ADMIN
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/token
X-API-KEY: chave-admin

### 5. Tentar com API Key inv√°lida (deve retornar 401)
